data.description: Must-See Bremen home in a peaceful country setting, featuring 3 parcels totaling 1.24 ac. Updates include a Gas Tankless Water Heater, Central AC, and a recently inspected roof. While it needs some TLC, the price accounts for cosmetic repairs and carpet replacement. New kitchen cabinets are included. Stainless steel electric stove, refrigerator, and washer-dryer under 2 years old are all yours. Enjoy a bonus LR with 3 gas-burning fireplaces, ample storage in the basement, and a partially finished room for office space. A gun safe is included, and the insulated 1-2 car garage comes with electric and heaters. New garage doors installed this year. Asphalt driveway. Fenced front yard with 3 double and 1 single gate. Schedule a showing soon & make this your new home for the Holidays!
